 images corresponding to views that are hard to uniquely\nidentify. For the latter we achieve the top results especially for symmetric\nobjects of ModelNet dataset.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 20 Dec 2020 19:20:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-22"}
