f commuting $d$ - tuples. We make a conjecture of what\nmight be a sharp bound in much greater generality and verify it in many\nexamples.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Dec 2020 04:52:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 20 Jan 2021 00:58:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-21"}
