y can\nconsider fixed-point implementation aspects that are disregarded by the\nstate-of-the-art verification methodologies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Dec 2020 10:03:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-22"}
